text: Pratihar, Pratihara or Parihar is a clan of Indian origin, It is found among the Gurjar, Rajput and Meena caste groups; *Pratihar Gurjars, Is a clan of Gurjar community found in Pakistan and India *Pratihar Rajputs, is a clan of Rajput caste of India *Pratihar Meena, clan of Meena caste
title: Pratihar
